# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values.
# `.env` is gitignored; this file (`.env.example`) is the checked-in template.

# PostgreSQL connection string used by Prisma (`prisma/schema.prisma`) and
# the repository layer (`src/repo/*.ts`). Provider is pinned to Postgres
# per OQ-3 — see README "Database (OQ-3 resolved)" and
# docs/api_and_database_design.md §9 OQ-3.
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/ga_scheduler_v2?schema=public"

# Optional — only set when running the SQLite/libSQL thesis-defense fallback.
# Switches src/repo/competencyCodec.ts to JSON-encode competency arrays.
# Requires regenerating migrations against a SQLite target first.
# DATABASE_PROVIDER="sqlite"
